guest_message: Hi there! I'm really excited to explore your menu. Could you tell me about your vegan options, especially any details on how they are prepared to avoid cross-contamination with animal products? I'm looking to order something with tofu and would love to know more!

Oh, the Vegetable Stir Fry sounds fantastic! I'd like to go with the hot spice level, please. Could you also make sure to add tofu as a protein option, and I'd love it with brown rice if possible. What's the price with those additions?
My name's Alex Turner. Thanks for getting my order right! I'm all set, so just the stir fry for now. Appreciate it!
